<ext_description linkend="Assembly_physical_requirement_allocation_mim.interface_component_allocation_constraint">
<note> This rule may not have been updated to agree with the changes in clause 4.2.</note><p>

The <b>interface_component_allocation_constraint</b> rule constrains the related
and relating  <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> of a  <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> when it
